@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oxvhrg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.13 * (v2 + (v2 + 0.96 - v1 + 0.04)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(0.75))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.50 - tmp + 0.95) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.47)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
